video.title: Cesar Millan's Leader of the Pack
video.synopsis: World-famous "Dog Whisperer" Cesar Millan uses his skills and knowledge to find good homes for seemingly unadoptable dogs.

episodes.synopsis: Cesar is determined to find a new pack leader for Rosie, a Staffie who's been in and out of shelters and developed some bad habits.
episodes.title: Rosie's Thorn

episodes.synopsis: Cesar must find a home for a large and strong Labrador crossbreed that scares potential adopters away when they come to his shelter.
episodes.title: Jet Power

episodes.synopsis: Cesar finds candidates who can give timid, fearful shelter dog Brigadiere what he needs: a leader with patience and understanding.
episodes.title: Love at First Bite

episodes.synopsis: Harry, an older basset hound, lands in a shelter when his owner passes away. Can Cesar find a family to take him in during his golden years?
episodes.title: When Harry Met Cesar

episodes.synopsis: Cesar must teach basic manners to Miles, a stray mutt with aggressive bad habits, so that he doesn't literally bite the hand that feeds him.
episodes.title: Miles to Go

episodes.synopsis: Cesar must find a new home for a greyhound named Amigo who's suffering with behavioral problems after being paired with the wrong family.
episodes.title: A Friend for Amigo

episodes.synopsis: Cesar is challenged to find a home for Janna, a 4-year-old female Belgian Malinois with an unusual behavior: self-mutilation.
episodes.title: Once Bitten

episodes.synopsis: Mambo, a terrier mix with a Napoleon complex, has so much energy that his old owners placed him in a shelter. Now it's up to Cesar to find him a home.
episodes.title: Mambo Madness

episodes.synopsis: Small dog Dora has big-time aggression, which makes her unattractive as a family pet. But Cesar thinks he can find her a home.
episodes.title: Dora's Dilemma

episodes.synopsis: Cesar steps in to save a German Shepherd named Mojo, who's having a hard time finding a home because of his barking and jumping.
episodes.title: Too Much Mojo

episodes.synopsis: Cesar uses the Dog Psychology Center to help Turbo, a mutt who's become far too aggressive after being chained up for most of his life.
episodes.title: Turbo Charged

episodes.synopsis: Cesar works to find a gentle and loving family for Sophia, a sweet dog who's lived her entire life in a shelter and is now afraid of humans.
episodes.title: Saving Sophia
